Hi. Miss... Miss Oher?

799
00:59:45,265 --> 00:59:48,496
- You from the state?
- No.

800
00:59:48,701 --> 00:59:51,727
My name is Leigh Anne Tuohy,
and your son...

801
00:59:52,071 --> 00:59:55,040
...Michael, lives with me...

802
00:59:55,708 --> 00:59:57,801
...and my family.

803
01:00:04,183 --> 01:00:07,209
